{"tid":1017034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來依家小巴一定要㩒鐘落車","createTime":"2019-02-11T07:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T08:35:28.000Z","uid":197940,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"095819463552634b2fafe71375d443197beae185","tid":1017034,"uid":197940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:45:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟今日搭左架綠色van仔，就到站個陣咪嗌有落囉，結果個司機飛左站，咁我咪只好再大聲d嗌前面個路口有落，諗唔到司機居然回左我一句 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要㩒鐘喎</span></span> 。好啦，作為一個毒撚嘅小弟只好死死氣氣地㩒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴打平時搭van仔係㩒鐘定嗌有落？<br />\n<br />\n利申：小巴公司話可以嗌有落同㩒鐘（毒撚樓主唔夠膽屌鳩個司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有去投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"bdfb31a31fc9a34713c3044176f0cf864fa7782a","tid":1017034,"uid":197940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43536ea830b205bbe1cbdfd3fd6f21aa5c8f5343","tid":1017034,"uid":14912,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:46:52.000Z","msg":"死毒撚唔會敢喊有落"},{"pid":"0b11ac9fedcfc0d7e1a4000abc3e03ebafda18b9","tid":1017034,"uid":197940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43536ea830b205bbe1cbdfd3fd6f21aa5c8f5343","tid":1017034,"ui